Invest AD Says It Hired Stephane Bwakira to Manage African Equities Fund

-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 
2011-03-21T09:02:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/invest-ad-says-it-hired-stephane-bwakira-to-manage-african-equities-fund.html
Invest AD, an Abu Dhabi government-
owned money manager, hired Stephane Bwakira to manage its Africa
equities fund.  Bwakira managed funds for Stanlib in  South Africa  and was
previously an equities analyst for Investec, Invest AD said in
an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  